Hello everyone...Well I&#039;ll get straight to the point.
What is your opinion on Akali...Every time I have an opponent Akali she will burst the s**t out of everyone while building tank items...Turret defence tactic doesn&#039;t seem to work against her unless you find a way to throw a stun...If she doesn&#039;t die before the stun wears off she can still burst and escape. Teamfights are very difficult as she does alot of damage on her own(as I noticed)...Okay I am VERY sure I am doing something wrong and the reason of this post is to receive help on how to play against Akali. Btw Akali is the only champion I struggle playing against...I MAINLY play support and my favourite champs are Taric and Alistar.

THANKS :D{{sticker:zombie-nunu-hearts}}
